      "id": "logic_coder_t",
      "x": 118,
      "y": 308,
      "width": 266.24,
      "height": 120.0,
      "text": "Decision logic (no LLM prompt):\n- mutate(): 6 random tweaks\n  (contrast, headline, cta, hue)\n- score = evals passed count\n- keep best of 6 candidates\n- NO per-eval fix logic",
      "originalText": "Decision logic (no LLM prompt):\n- mutate(): 6 random tweaks\n  (contrast, headline, cta, hue)\n- score = evals passed count\n- keep best of 6 candidates\n- NO per-eval fix logic",
