      "x": 658,
      "y": 308,
      "width": 291.2,
      "height": 120.0,
      "text": "Decision logic (no LLM prompt):\n- reads current Vision\n- rewrites headline + hue toward it\n- maxWords = 6 - brevity*3\n- hueTol = 40 - boldness*20\n- mints 2 new Evaluation objs",
