      "id": "r_synth_t",
      "x": 918,
      "y": 1008,
      "width": 307.84000000000003,
      "height": 160.0,
      "text": "Synthetic evals (minted at runtime by\nthe Reviewer agent):\n5. HeadlineBrevityEval(maxWords)\n     maxWords = 6 - brevity*3\n6. OnBrandHueEval(hue, tol)\n     tol = 40 - boldness*20\n\n(tightens as the Vision consolidates)",
      "originalText": "Synthetic evals (minted at runtime by\nthe Reviewer agent):\n5. HeadlineBrevityEval(maxWords)\n     maxWords = 6 - brevity*3\n6. OnBrandHueEval(hue, tol)\n     tol = 40 - boldness*20\n\n(tightens as the Vision consolidates)",
